snippet.title: Assassin's Creed Creator Shows First Gameplay From Ancestors: The Humankind Odyssey
snippet.description: Patrice Desilets, founder of Panache Digital Games, and former creator of the Assassin's Creed series before leaving Ubisoft, joins us to show an exclusive gameplay demo from the upcoming Ancestors: Humankind Odyssey.
